<text id="APB0313T">

<body>
<div1 type="summary">
<p>Boat repairs.</p>
</div1>

<div1 type="body">


<p>Dear <person_mentioned>Son</person_mentioned></p>

<p>Inclosed you have Notices which I recd <date_mentioned n="07-23-1818">yesterday</date_mentioned></p>

<p>I have your Boat now in a Situation that when the river falls a
little she will be ready to under go any reparees you may wish to
make to hir—</p>

<p>You <person_mentioned>Mother </person_mentioned>and myself think of starting to the <location_mentioned>mines </location_mentioned>on Sunday
if we can</p>

<p>I am Respectfully Yours</p>

<p><person_mentioned>Moses Austin</person_mentioned></p>

<p><location_mentioned>Herculanm   </location_mentioned><date_mentioned n="07-24-1818">July 24 1818</date_mentioned></p>

<p>[Addressed:] <person_mentioned>Mr James Bryan</person_mentioned>   <location_mentioned>Hazel Cottage</location_mentioned></p>
</div1>
